 The accident took place after 15:00 on Sunday afternoon, in which five people were killed.
Over 10 casualties were airlifted to Mpumalanga hospitals.  A medical helicopter touched down in Middelburg where two casualties were taken to Life Midmed Hospital, two more to the Middelburg Provincial Hospital and six others to Witbank.
